msgid "答：A9/A9G只支持物联网卡和移动4G手机卡，暂时不支持联通，电信等手机卡"
msgstr "A: A9/A9G only support IoT SIM cards and China Mobile 4G mobile SIM cards. China Unicom, China Telecom, and other mobile SIM cards are not supported for now."

