msgstr "No. It can only be done through two serial ports. One is the AT serial port, one is the download serial port, and one is the GPS serial port. The download serial port is only for downloading. Secondary development is supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:159 287a59f8d93742d991f90c9b6a649271
msgid "A9开发板供电可以极限是5.5V吗？5.28会有问题吗"
msgstr "Is the maximum power supply limit of the A9 development board 5.5V? Will 5.28V cause problems?"

