msgstr "5V. It may cause problems because the module power supply range is 3.8V to 4.2V. The USB port has a step-down circuit."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:163 a5f73e937c5b4b0ebff7a38e000b808f
msgid "A9G开发板可以刷NodeMCU 吗"
