msgid "不行哦"
msgstr "No."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:168 7c09c5485a5b4d4293708098a7637355
msgid "A9G模块能和3.3v的单片机直接相连吗？"
msgstr "Can the A9G module be directly connected to a 3.3V MCU?"

